caption.text:
Serena has no time for a migraine attack, which is why she treats with UBRELVY. Visit our website to see how UBRELVY quickly stops migraine in its tracks within 2 hours.

Please see full Patient Information here: http://bit.ly/2Q7wto0
-
UBRELVY is a prescription medicine used to treat migraine attacks in adults. It’s not for migraine prevention. Talk to your healthcare provider about UBRELVY and whether it’s right for you. There are risks with this product. Do not take with strong CYP3A4 inhibitors. Few people had side effects. The most common were nausea (2-4%) and tiredness (2-3%). In clinical studies, most people had pain relief and some had pain freedom within 2 hours.

caption.text:
Serena has no time for a migraine attack, which is why she treats with UBRELVY. Visit our website to see how UBRELVY quickly stops migraine in its tracks within 2 hours.

Please see full Patient Information here: http://bit.ly/2Q7wto0
-
UBRELVY is a prescription medicine used to treat migraine attacks in adults. It’s not for migraine prevention. Talk to your healthcare provider about UBRELVY and whether it’s right for you. There are risks with this product. Do not take with strong CYP3A4 inhibitors. Few people had side effects. The most common were nausea (2-4%) and tiredness (2-3%). In clinical studies, most people had pain relief and some had pain freedom within 2 hours.
